			<description>
				The Advanced_Boundary_Representation UoF specifies the definitional information 
				for the concept of an advanced boundary representation model. An advanced B-rep model 
				is a representation on one or more manifold_solid_breps each of which is defined with elementary 
				geometry or sculptured geometry.
